&lt;p&gt;Band 3 Senior Administrator Part Time, Fixed Term or Secondment Opportunity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Therapy Team is looking for a flexible, highly organised and self-motivated person to join our busy department at Mansfield Community Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen in our small friendly team in the rehabilitation suite for a Band 3 administrator covering a period of extended leave of at least 9 months. We provide therapy services in the outpatient and community settings, helping people with a variety of neurological and other health conditions to maximise their potential and independence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will have experience of NHS administration systems such as Systm1, Medway, NHS Supply Chain and will be forward thinking, multi-tasking, accurate, and able to work as part of a team as well as using their own initiative.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameFran PlattsJob titleTherapy Operational ManagerEmail addressfran.platts@nhs.netTelephone number01623785177Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sally Kennedy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Therapy Team Leader&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01623 785122 or sally.kennedy2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
